and its highly positive effects on the world of Islam prompted
the Zionist propaganda apparatus to embark on a passive campaign
to overshadow the fruitful outcome of the summit," the statement
said.
</P>
<P>
The Islamic Republic of Iran does not officially recognize
Israel and Iran broke off its relations with Tel Aviv after the
victory of the Islamic revolution in 1979.
</P>
<P>
"These familiar plys cannot halt the growing trend of
anti-Zionist sentiments and stances in the world of Islam," the
statement said. 
