<HEADLINE> Normal Functioning of Indian Airports to Be Resumed </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, December 25 (Xinhua) -- India's National Airport
Authority Officers Association (NAAOA) has asked all its members
to resume normal functioning at airports across the country, Press
Trust of India (PTI) said Thursday.
</P>
<P>
