should be fully aware of the necessity and difficulty of building
an efficient public security force, noting that a competent and
qualified police force is needed for the 21th century.
</P>
<P>
An official of the Ministry of Public Security said that over
the next two years, one million Chinese police officers will take
examinations and undergo assessment of their professional and
physical capabilities. Those who fail twice in the exams will be
dismissed from the police force.
</P>
<P>
By organizing regular training courses, the new exam system is
designed to improve the basic quality of the police
officers all over the country, the official said.  
