<HEADLINE> Pakistan Leaders Shocked over Train Tragedy </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, December 25 (Xinhua) -- Pakistani Prime Minister
Nawaz Sharif and Acting President Wasim Sajjad Thursday expressed
their heartfelt grief over the train tragedy that occurred late
Wednesday evening, claiming at least 34 lives.
</P>
