<HEADLINE> East China Province Developing Its Garments Industry </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HEHEI, December 25 (Xinhua) -- East China's Anhui Province
is trying to make its garments industry a pillar of its textile
industry and a new economic growth factor.
</P>
<P>
