<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, December 25 (Xinhua) -- Iran has named a new head for
the country's soccer federation, firing Dariush Mostafavi who had
caused controversy by trying to replace popular coach Valdeir
Vieira, newspapers said on Wednesday.
</P>
