the world's top 500 companies to invest more than 100 million
U.S. dollars.
</P>
<P>
The city has paid more attention to quality than quantity in
attracting overseas investment, and increased efforts to interest
international giants.
</P>
<P>
Guilin has improved its urban infrastructure during the last
few years, with a number of major projects launched in the past
six years mainly in telecommunications, water supply and drainage
systems.
</P>
<P>
