<HEADLINE> Shanghai Boosting Biological pharmaceutical Industry </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, December 25 (Xinhua) -- Shanghai Municipality has
decided to promote its modern biological pharmaceutical industry
in the coming three years.
</P>
<P>
The local government recently listed modern biological
pharmaceutical industry as one of the three high-technology
industries, which will be developed in an accelerated way.
</P>
<P>
In the first nine months of this year, the output value of the
industry reached 10 billion yuan (1.2 billion US dollars),
increasing 12 percent over the same period of last year.
</P>
