pharmaceutical products of the industry which take up about 30
percent on China's domestic market.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, Shanghai Municipality will invest more than one
billion yuan into the industry to study and manufacture new
products whose profit rate will exceed 70 percent.
</P>
<P>
Shanghai's modern biological pharmaceutical industry will
continue to seek cooperation with overseas counterparts.
</P>
<P>
Up to now, there are about 50 joint ventures in the industry
with 20 of them involving an investment of 10 million U.S. dollars
each.  
