century have emanated from misunderstandings between nations,
stressing the necessity to step up efforts on the threshold of a
new century to end misunderstandings through dialogues.
</P>
<P>
The Iranian president hailed the smooth development of the ties
between Iran and Sweden in economic, technical and cultural areas.
</P>
<P>
He added a considerable number of Iranians are living in the
northern European state and that most of them are highly educated
and considered good assets for bilateral cooperation.
</P>
<P>
The Swedish envoy said that Sweden attaches special importance
to the relations with Iran.
</P>
<P>
Terming the bilateral ties as excellent, Anderson said that the
two sides should make more efforts to boost their political and
economic cooperation. 
