businessmen didn't respond to the questionnaire distributed by
the BET. However, Buliki estimated that the figure exceeds last
year's 35.6 million Shillings (about 56,500 US Dollars).
</P>
<P>
The week-long fair starting from last Wednesday has attracted
some 8,000 visitors, far less than last year's figure of 187,000.
</P>
